{
  "texts": [
    "However, methods such as CoT combined with summarization do not significantly enhance performance, pointing to the ongoing challenges in free-response puzzle solving.",
    "Finally, MARB (Tong et al., 2023) encompasses a variety of riddle tasks.",
    "Several methodologies including zero-shot, CoT, IEP, and few-shot prompting are tested on models such as GPT-4 and PaLM2-540B (Anil et al., 2023).",
    "The combination of IEP and CoT emerged as the most effective method, highlighting the value of integrating multiple approaches for diverse riddle types.",
    "The dataset also includes commonsense puzzles (§4.2.3), showing similar trends with riddles."
  ]
}